    "title": "Mid-Level Frontend Developer at Broadcom India",
    "description": "Broadcom India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Frontend Developer for our Kochi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Broadcom India:\nBroadcom India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Broadcom India!",
